{"tid":1798362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國將再收緊限制 台積電或無法再為華為代工晶片","createTime":"2019-12-26T07:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T10:22:33.000Z","uid":25468,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d7092614a21fb68d455cd97bc207590f934fa0a2","tid":1798362,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pGkqWLagMH3RKqE7ZSZMFQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/iloveapps.com/57f29aba3fdce83127dbbf93bb6e1672\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpGkqWLagMH3RKqE7ZSZMFQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Filoveapps.com%2F57f29aba3fdce83127dbbf93bb6e1672&h=9f9db1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰看起來似乎已經平息，可暗地裡仍舊風潮湧動。根據台灣媒體的報導，美國已經開始阻斷台積電等非美國企業向華為供貨，計劃將「源自美國技術」的標準從 25%的比重，下調至10%。<br />\n<br />\n根據彭博、路透等媒體報導，台積電 7nm 工藝的美國技術佔比 9%~10% 之間，而 14nm 工藝的美國技術佔比超過 15%。外電報導稱經過台積電內部評估，7nm 工藝可以繼續供貨，14nm 可能受到限制。<br />\n<br />\n對此，華為旗下處理器公司海思，將處理器產品加速從 7nm 轉向 5nm，目前的 14nm 產品分散到中芯國際投產，用以避開美方牽制。<br />\n<br />\n台積電發言人稱在密切留意美國擴大對華為供貨限制，美國晶片企業、軟件企業正在積極與美國政府溝通，不希望做出傷害美國企業都措施。可目前沒有看到美國的正式措施，很難評論造成的影響，將正常提供代工服務。<br />\n<br />\n據悉美方可能於 2020年1月17日將標準下調自 10%，估到時對華為的影響更進一步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkstylemen.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%86%8D%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB-%E5%B0%87%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%86%8D%E5%B9%AB%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A214nm%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8-162157648.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkstylemen.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%25A9%258D%25E9%259B%25BB-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A214nm%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2599%25A8-162157648.html&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=cafdd60c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkstylemen.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%86%8D%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB-%E5%B0%87%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%86%8D%E5%B9%AB%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A214nm%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8-162157648.html</a>"},{"pid":"04788d371d1d3ebb07631efd5440935e5c7d5a3e","tid":1798362,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:21:41.000Z","msg":"梗係啦5nm<br />\n封咗哩一波新技術<br />\n屎為新手機一定慢對家一截"},{"pid":"6e648cad458f2a6fa5152231222d6f791db507cc","tid":1798362,"uid":18477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"用字煮燃法嘅28nm整咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924f41d8ecafab7d9d87552dce343c75bdeb3371","tid":1798362,"uid":7369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"其實慢慢禁先最撚吸血，每當共產黨搞好晒對策之後美國就封殺，加埋本身間公司仲要營運，咁搞法就等於雙重打擊！"},{"pid":"537ca9a385fedb16776298a5b782107ee1751b14","tid":1798362,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e648cad458f2a6fa5152231222d6f791db507cc","tid":1798362,"uid":18477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"用字煮燃法嘅28nm整咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:46:11.000Z","msg":"主要係28nm 以上唔駛面對量子領域，相對14/16nm 個物理難度低左，可以各施各法去實現。（28nm 未等如 805 個一代囉。）"},{"pid":"b40ed36400ea439636e8a4142bb189b001cd8ede","tid":1798362,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7092614a21fb68d455cd97bc207590f934fa0a2","tid":1798362,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pGkqWLagMH3RKqE7ZSZMFQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/iloveapps.com/57f29aba3fdce83127dbbf93bb6e1672\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k